release.name: v0.1.0
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Fix tests, remove amp by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/1
* Task/simplify content by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/2
* Feature/respect configured directories by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/10
* Add tests to CI by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/11
* Feature/build default config by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/13
* Feature/data import keyvaluestore by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/18
* Support events when content generated and written by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/19
* Allow content to be published and to include unpublished content base by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/20
* start work on rendered contents by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/22
* make sure final layout is formatted by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/23
* Add dot access, integrate annoated container by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/24
* Feature/docs container by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/28

## New Contributors
* @cspray made their first contribution in https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/pull/1

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/blogisthenics/commits/v0.1.0
